All the gas leaks scenario described in the document ¿ODH and CO2 risk assessment for the underground galleries of EHN2¿ shall be tested by simulation (EDMS 1972475)-	There are various solutions to mitigate the risk not to go lower than 18% of O2: (1) Take the new air from the surface level of the hall (then from the internal volume) and to reject the air inside the building: ¿internal loop¿ (2)	Take fresh air from outside and blow polluted air to outside of the building (3) Mix between those 2 solutions
A 3D model of the galleries is required to perform the calculation
